                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened] and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Unconscious] conditions from putrid plague can't end or be reduced until the disease is cured.</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[fortitude|dc:25]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effect (1d4 hours)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> sickened (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> unconscious (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> dead</p>"
