                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The gale frenzy combines its powers over the wind to draw prey closer. Each segment of the troop selects a different target within 20 feet; a targeted creature must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:28] save or be pulled adjacent to that segment of the troop. If a target was pulled off the ground and cannot fly, it then falls as normal.</p>"
