                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The gale frenzy swoops through an area with their talons arrayed in a harrowing wall of slashing peril as they rip at each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5]. Targets must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:25|basic|options:area-effect] save. The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d8+2)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage (plus putrid plague on a failure)</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(3d8+4)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage (plus putrid plague on a failure)</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(5d8+6)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage (plus putrid plague on a failure)</p>"
